  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In a large prospective cross-sectional study, the investigators aimed to identify the
      determinants of thyroid surgery outcomes and quantify the relative influence of preoperative
      and intraoperative factors. For this purpose, the investigators considered the interplay of
      several characteristics specific to surgeons, patients, and surgical procedures.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
